{"tid":2269852,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朴智宣與母陳屍家中 母親遺書曝光：我不能讓女兒一個人走","createTime":"2020-11-03T16:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T17:38:24.000Z","uid":203454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1042f1be4799b525c293e8d43ce8cb709ef33dce","tid":2269852,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"韓國女諧星朴智宣昨日被爆與母親陳屍家中，終年35歲，消息震驚演藝圈，而朴智宣與母親的靈堂現設於梨花女子大學木洞醫院。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：35歲韓女星朴智宣與母親陳屍家中 爸爸報警揭發悲劇<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日表示朴智宣家中沒有外部入侵等他殺的痕迹，推測兩人作出了極端的選擇，或會進行屍檢確認死因，不過今日警方就指，會尊重遺屬意願，將不會對朴智宣及其母親進行屍檢。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，朴智宣生前一直飽受陽光過敏的皮膚病的困擾，所以就算做了藝人亦以素顏出鏡，成為其特色。不過有消息指，朴智宣最近病情惡化，不論在戶外拍攝還是舞台燈光，都令她感到相當痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：朴智宣離世丨朴正民首位趕到靈堂送別 好友安英美缺席直播節目<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日在現場發現疑似朴智宣母親寫下的遺書，韓媒《朝鮮日報》將內容曝光：「女兒因皮膚病而非常痛苦，最近在治療其他疾病的過程中，令皮膚病更加惡化，亦感到更加痛苦。我不能讓女兒一個人走，老公對不起。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201103/KMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201103%2FKMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=d93d8efe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201103%2FKMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4%2F&h=1b6851c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201103/KMU3RL6FR5EJNNIDU53GQLVBA4/</a><br />\n<br />\n成件事好悲劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個阿媽真係好錫個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da184ba3ae41e05393f49eb77e260022b06e4931","tid":2269852,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739da0c055c1b6870aa573a450a96fc698fbcbfd","tid":2269852,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30681ec3697874e7bf2b7502678c40c49fa3458","tid":2269852,"uid":257330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed7649cb7297abeeb4a1d270bf8ebbd92a843a0","tid":2269852,"uid":141656,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"阿爸好慘<br />\n兩個至親一齊走<br />\n真係好大打擊"},{"pid":"b9b9670e92babd50331a8d7839de6b9d3a6b7239","tid":2269852,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:51:57.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"b6f9aa634953cccea826374a8549399c82067a24","tid":2269852,"uid":203454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ed7649cb7297abeeb4a1d270bf8ebbd92a843a0","tid":2269852,"uid":141656,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"阿爸好慘<br />\n兩個至親一齊走<br />\n真係好大打擊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"想像唔到阿媽有幾愛個女先會願意陪佢一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ea28d4ad10c030bd90392493dfe619f079c2ea","tid":2269852,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"因為個病唔曬得太陽真係好慘"},{"pid":"85c5b5617e4d35d830e963ea84da6f82ebb1de8e","tid":2269852,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T16:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32180fa19084f1f9180cfc5705104bf97443c754","tid":2269852,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:38:24.000Z","msg":"r.i.p...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk